{"tid":564571,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA︰超大黑洞迅速擴大 足以吞噬整個星系","createTime":"2018-02-18T06:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T07:37:09.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90ca5d516ab9d60af16d099d9aef63ef3543d1fd","tid":564571,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"美國太空總署（NASA）發現，一個超大黑洞增長得比預期快速，已超越了它們所在星系中新星形成的速度，這意味著宇宙中為數不少的黑洞比科學家原先估計的更大，而且可能逐漸吞噬它們所在的星系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180218/640_8a8cda846d9a82b016376341b933632a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180218%2F640_8a8cda846d9a82b016376341b933632a.jpg&h=27bb288b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n星球在即將衰亡時，會塌陷入自體之中，變成體積極小而密度極高的黑洞。大部份星系之中都會發現黑洞，黑洞會吸收周圍的所有物質，包括光、氣體甚至整個星系。<br />\n<br />\n之前的研究認為，黑洞以及星系中的星球數量是一起增長的，星系的大小不會影響黑洞的增長，但NASA的兩項調查發現，黑洞其實比星系中新星形成的速度更快。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180218/1300127/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180218%2F1300127%2F&d=0%2FjgaY9T%2BBAXZAwhpOOyonIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d99259c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180218%2F1300127%2F&h=59bbeddb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180218/1300127/</a>"},{"pid":"dab3a080f503794ccac51b91be95548ae0761fca","tid":564571,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"其中一個由賓州大學博士楊光（Guang Yang，音譯）進行的研究指出，「特大質量黑洞」（supermassive）在一個擁有1000億個太陽質量恆星的星系之中，其增長速度比起身處在約100億個太陽質量恆星的星系，足足快了10倍。"},{"pid":"5823e0df2f3829870aa44ae4011c04a780744c05","tid":564571,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"另一個由西班牙太空科學研究所進行的研究則調查了72個星系。負責調查的博士梅斯夸（Mar Mezcua）也說：「我們發現黑洞比預期的更大，&hellip;&hellip;它們可能更早就開始增長，又或者它們的增長速度已經持續了數十億年。」研究員調查的黑洞中，幾乎有一半黑洞的質量至少比太陽高100億倍。"},{"pid":"b7c944be1251a45adab76f58fbd01cf5422c2cb2","tid":564571,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大到理解唔到"},{"pid":"5c532ddcca2e48da4fc6ac4df617d9313b70af0d","tid":564571,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其中一個由「red」賓州[/red]大學博士楊光（Guang Yang，音譯）進行的研究指出，「特大質量黑洞」（supermassive）在一個擁有1000億個太陽質量恆星的星系之中，其增長速度比起身處在約100億個太陽質量恆星的星系，足足快了10倍。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a24807ea5d499b5ac623541b539a58b150b920ae","tid":564571,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c532ddcca2e48da4fc6ac4df617d9313b70af0d","tid":564571,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其中一個由「red」賓州[/red]大學博士楊光（Guang Yang，音譯）進行的研究指出，「特大質量黑洞」（supermassive）在一個擁有1000億個太陽質量恆星的星系之中，其增長速度比起身處在約100億個太陽質量恆星的星系，足足快了10倍。</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"唔好咁無聊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ba5d9efcc8164d133d7a3f80aafdc1c7242205","tid":564571,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a24807ea5d499b5ac623541b539a58b150b920ae","tid":564571,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c532ddcca2e48da4fc6ac4df617d9313b70af0d","tid":564571,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其中一個由「red」賓州[/red]大學博士楊光（Guang Yang，音譯）進行的研究指出，「特大質量黑洞」（supermassive）在一個擁有1000億個太陽質量恆星的星系之中，其增長速度比起身處在約100億個太陽質量恆星的星系，足足快了10倍。</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"唔好咁無聊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"而家少咗人叫做賓周<br />\n通常叫主主人"}]}